</head>

<div class="mainContainer">
    <h1>DbWebAPI</h1>
    <h5 style="text-align:center">ASP.Net Core Web Service Demo</h5>
    <br />
    <div style="text-align:left; width:100%;">
        <p>
            This demonstration API uses an in-memory database which holds an archive of mock
            food industry documents. The governments 'Food Standards Agency' require these
            documents to be archived and held by catering companies as a record, of their
            compliance with UK food hygiene regulation.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:left; width:100%;">
        <p>
            A Xamarin Mobile Application manages the business requirements of the regulation, 
            and uses the CRUD operations of this REST API to store and retrieve FSA documents
            from the remote server.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flexContainerRow clearfix blue">
        <div class="col1 flexContainerColumn sideBySide1col" style="margin:10% 0.5% 0.5% 0;">
            <h6>REST API</h6>
        </div>
        <div class="col11 flexContainerColumn">
            <hr />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flexContainerRow clearfix blue">
        <div class="col11 flexContainerColumn sideBySide10col" >
            <p>The OPEN API Controller exposes the Json Endpoints used by the Xamarin App for CRUD access to the Document Archive database. Written in C# and uses Nswag</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col1 flexContainerColumn sideBySide1col" >
            <button class="clearfix" title="Swagger Page"><a href="https://localhost:5001/swagger/index.html#/SCxItems">Nswag</a></button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flexContainerRow clearfix red">
        <div class="col1 flexContainerColumn sideBySide1col" style="margin:10% 0.5% 0.5% 0;">
            <h6>MVC View Pages</h6>
        </div>
        <div class="col11 flexContainerColumn">
            <hr />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flexContainerRow clearfix red">
        <div class="col11 flexContainerColumn sideBySide10col" >
            <p>Simple Modle-View-Controller web pages allow basic CRUD operations on database. Written in C#, HTML & CSS.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col1 flexContainerColumn sideBySide1col">
            <button class="clearfix" title="MVC View Pages"><a href="https://localhost:5001/Home/SCxView/Index">MVC</a></button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flexContainerRow clearfix green">
        <div class="col1 flexContainerColumn sideBySide1col" style="margin:10% 0.5% 0.5% 0;">
            <h6>Razor Pages</h6>
        </div>
        <div class="col11 flexContainerColumn">
            <hr />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flexContainerRow clearfix green">
        <div class="col11 flexContainerColumn sideBySide10col">
            <p>Razor web pages allow search & sort of document data and use a single popup modal to navigate the documents and execute Ajax CRUD requests. Written in C#, HTML, CSS & JavaScript.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col1 flexContainerColumn sideBySide1col" >
            <button class="clearfix" title="Razor Pages"><a href="https://localhost:5001/Home/SCxPage/Index">Razor</a></button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
